#: 21337012-0-2701
msgctxt "21337012-0-2701"
msgid ""
"Sir Marq,\n"
"\n"
"The <<z:1>> of \"\"High-King Emeric\"\" is dead. It happened during the "
"transfer. The wall crumbled and a troll grabbed the messenger. He was dead "
"before he knew what was happening.\n"
"\n"
"A High King allowing Orcs to rebuild Orsinium seems a great lie, but the "
"messenger would not alter his story despite repeated questioning. With the "
"messenger now dead, is there any hope of honorably ending our service?\n"
"\n"
"What hope is there for us now?\n"
"\n"
"Vigilance eternal,\n"
"Sir Emmath"
msgstr ""

